Class TaskManagerClientFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.adobe.idp.taskmanager.dsc.client.TaskManagerClientFactory

public class TaskManagerClientFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Factory class for for the following TaskManager client classes:

  • TaskManager for TaskManager
  • QueueManager for QueueManager
  • TaskManagerQueryService for the Task QueryService
  • TaskEndpoint for EndpointManager
  • EmailSettingService for EmailSettingService
